arStrings.szText: "The Herald we saw in Hell felt like a puppy compared to that beast."
(dry laugh) We should’ve put him down then.
The Soulstone was originally tailored for Astaroth – it was never meant to contain a Prime Evil. Mephisto was getting stronger and stronger inside of it. And the Herald with him.
It was only a sliver of him. But he is immortal – in a way, you killed a sliver of infinity. Next time, we’ll finish the job.
